  "Return a list of environment variables for Claude Code.
CLAUDE-BUFFER-NAME and DIRECTORY are provided by claude-code.
Returns a list of strings in the format \"VAR=value\"."
  ;; Example implementation - replace with your own:
  ;; You could read from a file, use auth-source, keychain, etc.
  (list
   "ANTHROPIC_MODEL=your-model-here"
   "AWS_REGION=your-region-here"
   "CLAUDE_CODE_USE_BEDROCK=true"
   "AWS_BEARER_TOKEN_BEDROCK=your-token-here"))

